Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,OP「HIBANA」
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.89,0:01:59.48,OP_JP_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(240,0)}産み落とされた孤独な世界で
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.48,0:02:03.31,OP_JP_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(0,240)}誰を信じて生きて行く？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.44,0:02:07.36,OP_JP_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}人とは何か　闇とは何か
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.36,0:02:10.28,OP_JP_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}飢えたこの目で睨んだ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.28,0:02:13.37,OP_JP_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}正気と忘我　くり返してる
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.37,0:02:18.45,OP_JP_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(0,360)}奈落の底で呼ぶ声響いた
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.45,0:02:24.54,OP_JP_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(240,0)}黄泉の路を漂う
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.54,0:02:29.47,OP_JP_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(0,240)}声にひかり差す
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.47,0:02:32.39,OP_JP_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(240,0)}守りたいもの
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.39,0:02:35.76,OP_JP_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(0,240)}変わらないまま
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.76,0:02:41.31,OP_JP_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(240,0)}精霊転化　絆を強さに
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.31,0:02:47.44,OP_JP_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}戦い続けよう　踠きながら
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.44,0:02:56.74,OP_JP_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}崩れそうでも　両手広げ叫んでいる
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.74,0:03:04.88,OP_JP_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(0,480)}火花を散らし　宿命を背負って
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.89,0:01:59.48,OP_CH_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(240,0)}誕生於孤獨的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.48,0:02:03.31,OP_CH_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(0,240)}我該信任著誰活下去？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.44,0:02:07.36,OP_CH_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不知何為人類  何為暗影
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.36,0:02:10.28,OP_CH_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}只得瞪圓飢渴的雙目
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.28,0:02:13.37,OP_CH_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}清醒與忘我  不斷重複著
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.37,0:02:18.45,OP_CH_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(0,360)}聽見奈落深處的呼喚
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.45,0:02:24.54,OP_CH_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(240,0)}飄蕩在黃泉之路
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.54,0:02:29.47,OP_CH_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(0,240)}我的聲音映照光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.47,0:02:32.39,OP_CH_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(240,0)}想要守護之物
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.39,0:02:35.76,OP_CH_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(0,240)}未曾改變過
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.76,0:02:41.31,OP_CH_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(240,0)}精靈轉化  化情誼為力量
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.31,0:02:47.44,OP_CH_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一同奮戰下去  只管堅持到底
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.44,0:02:56.74,OP_CH_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}即便搖搖欲墜  也要振臂高呼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.74,0:03:04.88,OP_CH_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(0,480)}火花燦爛迸放  身懷宿命前行
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,ED「夕闇のうた」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.58,0:22:17.98,ED_JP_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}光と影が手を取り駆け巡る
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.98,0:22:23.23,ED_JP_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}夜の中で生まれた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.57,0:22:30.78,ED_JP_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}小さな手のひらからこの世界に
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.78,0:22:33.94,ED_JP_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}愛を届けたい
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.41,0:22:40.22,ED_JP_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}荒れ果てた空の下に咲く
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.83,0:22:47.26,ED_JP_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}一番あかるい花びら
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.26,0:22:53.47,ED_JP_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}笑いさざめいて君と行く
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.47,0:22:59.86,ED_JP_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}時の中を
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.40,0:23:03.86,ED_JP_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}祈りのように
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.86,0:23:07.40,ED_JP_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}天と土を結ぶ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.40,0:23:12.61,ED_JP_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,960)\blur3}君がうたう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.80,0:23:36.96,ED_JP_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}静かなうた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.58,0:22:17.98,ED_CH_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}光影交織巡迴之間
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.98,0:22:23.23,ED_CH_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}你降生於夜幕
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.57,0:22:30.78,ED_CH_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}小小的手掌向著廣大世界
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.78,0:22:33.94,ED_CH_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}播撒愛的種子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.41,0:22:40.22,ED_CH_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}荒天之下唯獨綻放著
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.83,0:22:47.26,ED_CH_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}那一輪最明亮的花
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.26,0:22:53.47,ED_CH_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}歡聲笑語中與你同行
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.47,0:22:59.86,ED_CH_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}走過時間
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.40,0:23:03.86,ED_CH_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}如同心願一般
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.86,0:23:07.40,ED_CH_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}天地走向大同
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.40,0:23:12.61,ED_CH_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,960)\blur3}只因你的歌聲
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.80,0:23:36.96,ED_CH_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}靜謐之歌
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,
